description:
Join Super Star Panda on its big space adventure now!

Beat numerous levels by showing skills and planning. Evade obstacles, deadly rockets, and cosmic lasers.

Unlock new heroes as you progress through more and more challenging planets.

Collect stars and power-ups along your journey unlocking exciting new galaxies.

This simple, yet challenging arcade game will have you trying and having "one more time" moments over and over again!

Enjoy with your children! It is violence-free fun for everyone to play and master.

See you in space!
name: Super Star Panda
intro: A classic arcade game, from young and old - for old and young.
